sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as ML Client<br/>(Python SDK)
    participant Browser as Browser<br/>(React UI)
    participant Gateway as Platform Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Proxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MLflow as MLflow Server<br/>5000/TCP HTTP
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP
    participant S3 as S3/MinIO<br/>9000/TCP HTTPS
    participant LLM as LLM Provider<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OTEL as OTEL Agent

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: Experiment Run Tracking
    Client->>Gateway: POST /api/2.0/mlflow/runs/create<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (JWT)
    Gateway->>Proxy: Forward (TLS 1.2+)
    Proxy->>Proxy: Validate JWT via Kubernetes RBAC
    Proxy->>MLflow: Forward (HTTP localhost)
    MLflow->>MLflow: Check workspace-scoped RBAC
    MLflow->>PG: INSERT run record<br/>Auth: Password
    PG-->>MLflow: Run ID
    MLflow-->>Proxy: 200 OK (Run metadata)
    Proxy-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1b: Log Artifact
    Client->>Gateway: POST /api/2.0/mlflow/runs/log-artifact<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Gateway->>Proxy: Forward (TLS 1.2+)
    Proxy->>MLflow: Forward (HTTP)
    MLflow->>S3: PUT artifact<br/>Auth: AWS Access Key<br/>Encryption: TLS 1.2+
    S3-->>MLflow: 200 OK
    MLflow->>PG: UPDATE artifact metadata
    PG-->>MLflow: OK
    MLflow-->>Client: 200 OK

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1c: Log Metrics/Parameters
    Client->>Gateway: POST /api/2.0/mlflow/runs/log-batch<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Gateway->>Proxy: Forward
    Proxy->>MLflow: Forward
    MLflow->>PG: INSERT metrics, params<br/>Auth: Password
    PG-->>MLflow: OK
    MLflow-->>Client: 200 OK

    Note over OTEL,PG: Flow 2: OTLP Trace Ingestion
    OTEL->>MLflow: POST /v1/traces<br/>Content-Type: application/x-protobuf<br/>Auth: None (OTLP standard)
    MLflow->>PG: INSERT trace spans<br/>Auth: Password
    PG-->>MLflow: OK
    MLflow-->>OTEL: 200 OK

    Note over Client,LLM: Flow 3: AI Gateway LLM Proxy
    Client->>Gateway: POST /gateway/{endpoint}/invocations<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (JWT)
    Gateway->>Proxy: Forward (TLS 1.2+)
    Proxy->>MLflow: Forward (HTTP)
    MLflow->>MLflow: Check gateway RBAC
    MLflow->>LLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Auth: API Key (Bearer)<br/>Encryption: TLS 1.2+
    LLM-->>MLflow: LLM Response
    MLflow-->>Client: Proxied Response

    Note over Browser,PG: Flow 4: React UI Interaction
    Browser->>Gateway: POST /graphql<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (JWT)
    Gateway->>Proxy: Forward (TLS 1.2+)
    Proxy->>MLflow: Forward (HTTP)
    MLflow->>PG: SELECT experiments, runs, models
    PG-->>MLflow: Query results
    MLflow-->>Browser: GraphQL JSON Response
